OL,3,CIndependent police force to review
OL,4,CMet's handling of Stephen Lawrence case
OL,6,FAn independent police force will
OL,7,Freview the Metropolitan Police's
OL,8,Fhandling of new evidence regarding the
OL,9,Fmurder of 30 years after his death,
OL,10,Fthe mayor of London has said.
OL,12,FIt comes after Met Commissioner Sir
OL,13,FMark Rowley apologised to Mr
OL,14,FLawrence's mother Baroness Doreen
OL,15,FLawrence for not fulfilling a promise
OL,16,Fto answer questions stemming from a
OL,17,FBBC investigation into the murder of
OL,18,Fthe 18-year-old in 1993.
