OL,3,CIndependent police force to review
OL,4,CMet's handling of Stephen Lawrence case
OL,6,FThe BBC said Lady Lawrence was
OL,7,Fpromised an explanation after the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster named Matthew White as the
OL,9,Fsixth suspect in the case last year.
OL,11,FMr Lawrence was murdered by a gang of
OL,12,Fracists in Eltham, south-east London,
OL,13,Fin April 1993 as he ran to catch a bus
OL,14,Fwith his friend Duwayne Brooks.
OL,16,FOnly two of his killers ` Gary Dobson
OL,17,Fand David Norris ` have ever been
OL,18,Fbrought to justice.
