OL,3,CIndependent police force to review
OL,4,CMet's handling of Stephen Lawrence case
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Met said:
OL,7,F"While we have not identified any
OL,8,Fadditional viable lines of inquiry,
OL,9,Frecognising the concerns held by
OL,10,FBaroness Lawrence and the significance
OL,11,Fof this investigation we will be
OL,12,Fasking an outside force to review our
OL,13,Fapproach."
OL,15,FThe original investigation into Mr
OL,16,FLawrence's death was hampered by
OL,17,Finstitutional racism in the Met, and
OL,18,Fclaims that corrupt officers had
OL,19,Fsought to protect Norris, whose father
OL,20,FClifford Norris was a notorious drug
OL,21,Fdealer.
