OL,3,CIndependent police force to review
OL,4,CMet's handling of Stephen Lawrence case
OL,6,FLast June, the BBC named White, who
OL,7,Fdied aged 50 in 2021, and outlined the
OL,8,Fbungled handling of evidence against
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FTwo witnesses said White had confessed
OL,12,Fto being present during the attack and
OL,13,Fone, his stepfather, was not spoken to
OL,14,Fby police until 20 years after the
OL,15,Fmurder because officers had previously
OL,16,Fmisidentified him.
OL,18,FWhite was arrested twice in connection
OL,19,Fwith the murder, but on both occasions
OL,20,Fthere was not enough evidence for a
OL,21,Fprosecution, the Met said.
