OL,3,CIndependent police force to review
OL,4,CMet's handling of Stephen Lawrence case
OL,6,FSir Mark said: "We recognise this is a
OL,7,Fparticularly difficult time for the
OL,8,FLawrence family and Duwayne Brooks. I
OL,9,Fam sorry our failure to respond in a
OL,10,Ftimely fashion has added to this.
OL,12,F"On top of the failures over the
OL,13,Fdecades this is totally unacceptable.
OL,15,F"Restoring trust in the Met is one of
OL,16,Fmy top priorities and that includes
OL,17,Fhow we work with those affected by the
OL,18,Ffailures of the past.
